#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""Remote dictation server — whisper.cpp over HTTP with a web UI.

Phone records audio in the browser, POSTs it to this server,
which runs whisper-cli (GPU-accelerated) and returns text.
Optionally formats as RP via claude-code-proxy.

Usage:
    dictation-server [--port PORT] [--host HOST] [--no-ssl]
"""

